    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">Per manus <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>i ep<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>sc</abbr><ex>op</ex><abbr>i</abbr></expan> V <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> I<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>dep</abbr><ex>ositio</ex></expan> memoriae beati Pet</supplied><expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex cert="low"/>i</expan> apostoli Α <expan><abbr>PX</abbr><ex>Christus</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">Ω</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ergänzungen und Datierung nach Egger: Z. 1 Anfang: [Hoc loco sancto instantia Symfer]i(?), 400 n. Chr.; Z. 3: [Stilichone v(iro) c(larissimo) co(n)s(ule)]; Bulić - Bervaldi: Z. 2: [depositio reliquiarum beati Petr]i. Textwiedergabe nach Marin u. a. Z. 2 (Ende): Hedera und Christogramm zwischen A u. [Ω]. Neun aneinander passende Fragmente.</p>
            </div>
